<document xml:lang="smj">
    <header>
        <title>Installing, configuring and switching keyboards in
        Windows 10</title>
    </header>
    <body>
      <section>
      <title>Installation</title>
        <ol>
          <li>Go to the <a
            href="http://divvun.no/no/keyboards/desktopindex.html">Divvun
            keyboard download page</a>, and click on the
            <strong>download link for Windows 10</strong>:
            <p><img src="images/win10/01_download-sme-en.png"
            alt="Download"/></p>
          </li>
          <li><strong>Run</strong> the downloaded installer:
            <p><img src="images/win10/02_run-installer-sme-en.png"
            alt="Run installer"/></p>
          </li>
          <li><strong>Allow</strong> the installer to make changes:
            <p><img src="images/win10/03_allow_changes-sme-en.png"
            alt="Allow changes"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Select installer language:
            <p><img src="images/win10/04_select_inst_lang-sme-en.png"
            alt="Select installer language"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Choose install location, the default is fine:
            <p><img src="images/win10/05_inst_location-sme-en.png"
            alt="Installation location"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Select Start Menu location, the default is fine:
            <p><img src="images/win10/06_start_menu-sme-en.png"
            alt="Start menu"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>You are now ready to install:
            <p><img src="images/win10/07_ready_to_install-sme-en.png"
            alt="Ready to install"/></p>
            <p><img src="images/win10/08_installing-sme-en.png"
            alt="Installing"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>You have to <strong>Restart</strong> after installation to ensure
            the keyboard is working properly:
            <p><img src="images/win10/09_restart-sme-en.png" alt="Restart"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>After the restart, the new keyboard(s) should show up in the
            keyboard menu (if not, continue as described below):
            <p><img src="images/win10/10_keyboard_menu-sme-en.png"
            alt="Keyboard menu"/></p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>
      <section>
      <title>Configuration</title>
        <p>The installation done above should automatically have turned on the
        installed keyboards. In case it has not happened, or you want to change
        the configuration, do as follows:</p>
  
        <ol>
          <li>Maná <strong>Start</strong>-menijjaj, ja dieddelaste
              <strong>Innstillinger</strong>:
              <p><img src="images/win10/start_menu-no.png" alt="Startmeny"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Maná <strong>Klokkeslett og språk</strong>:
              <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-no.png" alt="Kontrollpanel"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Dieddela <strong>Legg til et språk</strong>:
              <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-time_and_lang-no.png"
              alt="Språk" /></p>
          </li>
          <li>Válljitjit <strong>Julevsámegielav</strong> dieddelaste:
              <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-smj-no.png"
              alt="Legg til språk"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Vállji makkir <strong>Julevsámegiella</strong> dunji hiehpá:
              <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-smj-norway-no.png"
              alt="Regionale varianter"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Markieri <strong>Julevsámegiella</strong> ja dieddela
              <strong>Alternativer</strong>:
              <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-modify-smj-no.png"
              alt="Språk etter å ha valgt nordsamisk"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Dieddela <strong>Legg til tastatur</strong>:
              <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-keyboard-smj-no.png"
              alt="Språkalternativer"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Vállji <strong>Samisk, utvidet Norge</strong>:
              <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-smj-extended-norway-no.png"
              alt="Inndatametode"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Markieri <strong>Norsk med samisk</strong> ja dieddela
              <strong>Fjern</strong>:
              <p><img
              src="images/win10/prefs-remove-norw_with_sami-keyboard-smj-no.png"
              alt="Språkalternativer: Fjern norsk med samisk"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>De la dujna <strong>Julevsámegiela (Vuodna)</strong>
              tjállemgiellan
              boallonbievdijn <strong>Samisk, utvidet Norge</strong>:
              <p><img src="images/win10/keyboard-done-smj-no.png"
              alt="Språk med nordsamisk ferdigvalgt"/></p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>
      <section>
      <title>Switching keyboards</title>
        <ol>
          <li>Målsotjit boallobievdij, ja navti aj gielaj gaskan, dieddelaste 
              <strong>Windows+gasska</strong> dasik julevsáme boallobievdde l
              anon:
              <p><img src="images/win10/switching-keyboards-smj-no.png"
              alt="Språk med nordsamisk ferdigvalgt"/></p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>
    </body>
</document>
